@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dmbuva(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v0 * tmp)
    tmp = (0.03 * (v2 - wp.cos(v1 + 0.02)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.10 / v0 + 0.60)) * v2)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.30) / (v2 + 0.35 / v0 + 0.13)) / v1)
    v1 = (v2 + (v0 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.59)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.16 * v2 + 0.98)) / ((v2 + 0.25 - v2 + 0.10) * (tmp + 0.41 * v2 + 0.81)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v2 + 0.18 / v0 + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
